Example Makefile that is compatible with generate-help.awk

This Makefile simplifies porting configuration to new systems.

	[36mall            [0m  Generate all derived files (currently only embed)
	[36membed          [0m  Generate the embeddable target and recipe
	[31minstall        [0m  Install this file to the system
	[36mclean          [0m  Remove generated files
	[36mhelp           [0m  Generate this help message

Please let me know if you find this project useful. Open an issue should
something not work as expected or should you have an enhancement idea.

Targets in [31mred[0m might require sudo.
